      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS GLAMOURPUSS (5) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (20.81) when third at Nowra in a NG. Looks the one to beat with even luck. KOORINGA EXPRESS (3) has a strong record here with four wins and four placings from 12 starts. Comes off a (22.52) win last time, scoring by 2.25 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 400m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. TUMBY BAY (2) was on speed settling but found some traffic when checked, missing the frame to finish eighth (23.69) at The Gardens in a Grade 5. Expected to feature on best form. MAXIMUM ACE (1) placed last start at big odds and is in the mix again.",
